- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is another possible category as the model is evaluated on image caption generation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also be applicable as the paper proposes a new neural sequence model. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is less likely but still possible as the proposed model is a neural network-based approach.
